  "intent_precise": "Thermocycler 4Plates 384PCR 12PrimesSets-32cDNAsQuad: Using tc_plate (pcr_plate, slot 2), plate (plate, slot 9). With Thermocycler Module module. (1) Close thermocycler lid. (2) Set temperature to 4\u00b0C. (3) Operate thermocycler. (4) Wait 1 seconds. (5) Wait 1 seconds. (6) Wait 1 seconds. (7) Wait 1 seconds. (8) Wait 1 seconds. (9) Wait 1 seconds. (10) Wait 1 seconds. (11) Wait 1 seconds. (12) Wait 1 seconds. (13) Wait 1 seconds. (14) Wait 1 seconds. (15) Wait 1 seconds. (16) Wait 1 seconds. (17) Wait 1 seconds. (18) Wait 1 seconds. (19) Wait 1 seconds. (20) Wait 1 seconds. (21) Wait 1 seconds. (22) Wait 1 seconds. (23) Wait 1 seconds. (24) Wait 1 seconds. (25) Wait 1 seconds. (26) Wait 1 seconds. (27) Wait 1 seconds. (28) Open thermocycler lid. (29) Wait 1 seconds. (30) Wait 1 seconds.",
